title: DEFENSE OF MOUNT GRAM - Third Age Total War Gameplay
description:
Third Age Total War Gameplay - The Dwarves have a home away from home in the Blue Mountains at Mount Gram.  Unfortunately the mountain is near Angmar and the Witch king is on the rise!  After a failed attempt, the witch king is sieging Mount Gram once again!  Will the dwarves successfully defend their homes?  Enjoy the battle :D

Battle Made by KuroGuroChan
